data.description: WOW - LOOK AT WHAT THIS HOME OFFERS!! Beautiful 3-BR home with open  floorplan, custom interior paint, tile flooring except BR's, custom tile floor in living room, hardwood flooring in master & 2nd bedroom. Granite counter tops upgraded appliances plus pantry in kitchen and a spacious dining area.  2'' blinds throughout plus more, energy saving ceiling fans, sunscreens, and OWNED SOLAR, as seller is paying it off at closing.  DBL vanity in master bath plus a good size walk in closet. Mirrored closet doors in bedrooms. The back yard features a huge extended patio with part of it covered. 3 large fruit bearing citrus trees, orange, grapefruit, and lemon. Low maintenance landscaping front and back plus block fence, tile roof, 2 car garage, RV gate and RV parking.  No HOA, and a great locat
